HEADWORD: Trachinoid
<hw>Tra"chi*noid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or like, <gen>Trachinus</gen>, a genus of fishes
which includes the weevers. See <er>Weever</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

